      <p>
        <Bi
          zh="4-4-4-6 村莊在 Lv5 田時每小時產 828 資源（Lv10 = 5,040/hr）。前 7 天田還在升級中，平均產量 ≈ 500-1500/hr。策略的「資源/hr」需求超過這個就要靠 farming 補。"
          en="A 4-4-4-6 village produces 828/hr at field Lv5 (Lv10 = 5,040/hr). Over the first 7 days fields ramp up, averaging 500–1,500/hr. Whenever strategy demand exceeds production, you must cover the gap via farming raids."
        />
      </p>
      <Callout kind="tip" titleZh="Farming 的真正價值" titleEn="Why farming actually matters">
        <p>
          <Bi
            zh="不是「總資源不夠」（13 天平均田產其實夠用），而是「時機」：Day 1-3 田還在 Lv1-3，每小時幾百資源根本不夠蓋下一棟建築。Clubswinger × 6 每小時 raid 約 500-1000 資源 = 讓你早 2-3 天進入 Lv5-10 田階段。這才是 4P-farm 比 4P-sim 早開村的關鍵。"
            en="It's not that you 'run out of resources overall' (average production over 13 days is technically enough). It's timing: in Days 1–3 fields are Lv1–3, producing only a few hundred per hour — far too slow to keep queuing buildings. Six Clubswingers raiding yields ~500–1,000/hr, which pulls your Lv5–10 field milestone forward by 2–3 days. That's why 4P-farm settles before 4P-sim."
          />
        </p>
      </Callout>

      <h3><Bi zh="策略可行性驗證" en="Strategy feasibility check" /></h3>
