          ['3P Farming', '1,737', '890', '+848',  { zh: '需 farming ~850/hr', en: 'Needs farming ~850/hr' }],
          ['Lazy Decent','717',   '891', '−174',  { zh: '自產即可（慢但穩）', en: 'Self-sufficient (slow but safe)' }],
        ]}
      />
      <Callout kind="warn" titleZh="「Sim」不等於「完全不 farm」" titleEn="'Sim' does not mean 'zero farming'">
        <p>
          <Bi
            zh="Sim 策略 Gap 還是 +977 ~ +1,192/hr — 這份資源靠英雄打綠洲、每日任務、鄰居 raid 空 inactives、保護期獎勵補。真正「純 sim」只有 Lazy Decent。Carpis xlsx 的「Sim」是指「不訓專屬 farm 兵」，不是「完全不搶資源」。"
            en="The Sim path still has a +977–1,192/hr gap — covered by hero oasis raids, daily tasks, sniping inactive neighbors, and beginner-protection rewards. The only truly self-sufficient path is Lazy Decent. xlsx's 'Sim' means 'no dedicated farming troops', not 'no resource grabbing'."
          />
        </p>
      </Callout>
      <p>
        <Bi
          zh="社群已知 xlsx 外的替代路線：(1) 2-party rush Day 8-9 chief，但需大量 gold/farming；(2) Hero-farm path（Lv10 Mansion + 綠洲）— 未嚴格證明最優；(3) Gold-instant 5min 免費規則已被移除，目前均需金幣。Carpis xlsx 5 條算涵蓋主流無金幣免費打法。"
          en="Community alternatives NOT in xlsx: (1) 2-party rush → Day 8–9 chief but requires heavy gold/farming; (2) Hero-farm path (Lv10 Mansion + oases) — not rigorously proven optimal; (3) Gold-instant 5-min free rule was removed — all instant completions now cost gold. xlsx's 5 strategies reasonably cover mainstream no-gold free play."
        />
      </p>

