      <h3><Bi zh="忠誠度與征服（Chiefing）" en="Loyalty & chiefing" /></h3>
      <p>
        <Bi
          zh="每個村莊有忠誠度（loyalty）值。預設 100，被攻擊 + 參議員/司令官/族長/州長/重步兵/五長官/首領 同行時會降低。降至 0 = 易主。每場大型慶典把基線拉到 +25（共 125），這就是為什麼鐵砧主動辦慶典的原因。"
          en="Every village has a loyalty value, defaulting to 100. It drops when attacked by an army containing a chief unit (Senator/Chief/Chieftain/Nomarch/Logades/Ephor/Jarl). At 0 the village changes hands. A great celebration raises the baseline to 125 — that's why anvils proactively run them."
