          [{ zh: '首領 (Jarl, 維京人)', en: 'Jarl (Viking)' }, '15–30%', { zh: '維京人英雄的 raid 忠誠傷害是獨立機制，不計入首領（Jarl）的擲骰', en: "Viking hero's raid loyalty damage is a separate mechanic, not part of Jarl's roll" }],
        ]}
