        />
      </p>
      <Callout kind="warn" titleZh="防守忠誠度的工具" titleEn="Defending loyalty">
        <p>
          <Bi
            zh="忠誠藥水（Tablet of Law，從冒險取得）：每用 1 個恢復 1% 忠誠。被精準連擊（.00 / .01 兩波）時，要在 .00 之前喝。可同時計時建造行宮/皇宮，等它們在 wave 中間完工 → 立刻把忠誠度回滿。"
            en="Loyalty Tablets (from adventures) restore 1% loyalty per use. Against tightly-timed waves (e.g., .00 + .01), drink BEFORE .00. You can also time a Residence/Palace upgrade to finish in the gap between waves — completion instantly restores loyalty."
          />
        </p>
